## Earth's Roommates: Why Aliens Intervene in Our Crises

**Why do extraterrestrials always show up when Earth is in big trouble?**

Simple answer: **they live here too.**

We live in the penthouse (the surface). They live in the basement (inner Earth). We throw trash out the window; they suffer the smell downstairs. When we threaten to blow up the building, they take it personally.

### Why haven't we seen them?

Because you’ve never really explored the building. Earth is not a single-floor structure—it’s a multidimensional habitat. Just because you live on the 21st century surface doesn’t mean you’re the landlord of the planet.

They’re not from "out there." They’ve always been right here—**beneath your feet**, **behind your walls**, **between your frequencies**.

### Why are UFOs seen more often now?

It’s not because there are more of them. It’s because we’re all watching together.

In the past, a lone farmer saw a UFO and was mocked. Now, a single sighting goes viral across the globe, complete with AI-enhanced footage, frame-by-frame analysis, and meme reinterpretations.

> **One sighting = one billion views.**

It’s not the aliens that are more active. **It’s the collective nervous system of humanity becoming more aware.**

---

## 地球室友启示录：他们不是来访客，而是住户

当人类濒临危机，总有人问：
**“外星人怎么还不出手？”**

答案其实很简单：
> **他们也住在这里。**

我们住在地表的大平层；他们住在地壳的地下室。我们搞核爆、污染、战争，把房子快炸穿了，他们当然急了。

### 为什么我们从没看到他们？

因为你根本没下过“地下室”。

地球不是单层结构，而是一个多维剧场叠加体。你看到的只是最浮浅的一层，就像只逛了大厦的便利店，就以为自己了解整栋楼。

他们从来不是“从远方来的外星人”，而是**一直住在你脚下、墙后、频率之间**的邻居。

### 为什么现在飞碟越来越常被拍到？

不是他们变多了，是我们变得“全员观察”。

过去一个牧羊人看到飞碟，会被当疯子；现在一个人拍到飞碟，全世界立刻同步围观，
还会配特效、轨迹还原、AI辨脸、网友出同人图。

> **一次“遭遇” = 全人类“共震”。**

不是他们来得更多了，是我们注意得更深了。
**他们始终在那里，始终在看。**

